data.description: Live in historic Panama Park! Beautiful 3 bed 1 bath home with separate living and dining space. Original hardwood floors have been recently redone. Brand new roof installed in 2023, new hot water heater, updated electrical and plumbing, plus new paint inside and out! Conveniently located with less than a 15 minute ride whether you're headed to the airport, the Jaguar stadium, the Zoo or River City Marketplace. This home is a MUST SEE.
